node.text:
The idea for BURNOUT initiated in the peak of the 2020 pandemic. It was created as an expression of all that was happening. Wildfires, Pandemic, Isolation, Protests, Torture, Deaths, Marches, Personal losses, Grievances, Change. It feels as if we are undergoing a worldwide transformation- a rebirth of some kind. We are being made aware of broken systems, of the deep faults in our society, of a rumbling under the surface we have long been ignoring.  When everything else is in flames all we have is love, connections, empathy. We have each other. This is our power. It is a reminder that when our flames are extinguished and this is all over, we can look beyond ourselves. We can build bridges and empathy to the worlds still in fumes. 

Created by @shannonhaly, @jamesmulmusic and @carmenkovacs_ 

Directed and performed by @ebinumbrothers

Lyrics and performance by @shannonhaly

Music written and produced by @jamesmulmusic

Cinematography by @slimshowroom
